Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.97,0:00:22.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼一直要追我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.77,0:00:24.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到底是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.66,0:00:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.23,0:01:51.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.30,0:01:58.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那孩子很有素質吧 次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.57,0:02:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過他的力量還沒露出來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.24,0:02:03.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你看怎樣 要試他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.38,0:02:05.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,試他？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.51,0:02:07.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就挑學校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.05,0:02:10.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是誰在攻擊我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.72,0:02:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,城市為何變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.60,0:02:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,難道 剛才我看到的的女孩是幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.89,0:04:12.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,片名：夜來了(1)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.92,0:04:35.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.52,0:04:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,葉村涼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.66,0:04:40.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.60,0:04:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我有事跟你談
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.73,0:04:50.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,夜裡七點在第二校舍屋頂見
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.00,0:04:51.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.29,0:05:02.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等一下 餵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.89,0:05:04.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,妳們的目的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.89,0:05:05.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.10,0:05:07.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別動粗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.96,0:05:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這麼任性 是她拜託妳們的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.10,0:05:14.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不好意思 葉村涼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.30,0:05:17.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們祇是試一下你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.11,0:05:19.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,力量？什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.98,0:05:23.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,昨天 你避開交通標誌時的敏銳直覺
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.46,0:05:25.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還有避開我的攻擊的身手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.72,0:05:27.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是不知不覺中 使用“力量”的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.26,0:05:29.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟我們一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.13,0:05:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,昨天...是指...？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.33,0:05:36.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等 妳們在鬧什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.54,0:05:38.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快把人帶過來呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:48.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是葉村涼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.55,0:05:50.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是天文部部長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.36,0:05:52.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小倉泉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.63,0:05:56.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜託你 跟我們一起戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.23,0:06:00.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他們...到底是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.91,0:06:14.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個...我不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.72,0:06:16.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你說妳們是天文部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.59,0:06:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而那祇是 用來滿混世人耳目的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.00,0:06:22.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其實 妳們是叫做“火蛇”的戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:24.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,從藍色月亮過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.60,0:06:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在對抗昨天攻擊我的怪物的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.94,0:06:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.61,0:06:33.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,了不起 馬上理解部長講的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.68,0:06:35.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這種人頭次遇到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.81,0:06:37.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我很不會解釋的...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.22,0:06:41.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,葉村 再來喝一杯茶如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.62,0:06:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.96,0:06:46.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,總之發生太多事了 我有點摸不著頭緒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.30,0:06:49.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讓我考慮一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.91,0:06:51.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,葉村
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.78,0:06:56.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.65,0:06:59.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可否 請你在一星期內給我答覆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.58,0:07:03.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果你不想 跟今天談論的事物扯上關係
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.32,0:07:06.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到時我們就會消除你的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.46,0:07:09.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,消除記憶？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.81,0:07:24.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吵死了 笨女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.08,0:07:28.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別這樣不要在意她就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.29,0:07:30.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是你不覺得發毛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.42,0:07:32.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真拿您這個人沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.63,0:07:38.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她出了點事 所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.11,0:07:42.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,破壞掉算了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.73,0:07:59.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.40,0:08:02.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雨好煩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.00,0:08:04.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,最近公園有個女色狼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.28,0:08:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,討厭 你別老是在網上混了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.42,0:08:12.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.09,0:08:22.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是我們班的...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:26.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,後藤？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.06,0:08:45.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.99,0:08:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,葉村 我是小倉泉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.53,0:08:50.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,前幾天提的事你考慮過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.07,0:08:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,呃...我還沒做好決定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.27,0:08:59.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.61,0:09:02.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今夜請到公園來好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.82,0:09:03.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.89,0:09:07.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想讓你看看 敵人是什麼樣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.96,0:09:11.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.97,0:09:18.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,後藤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.97,0:10:01.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,學長...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.38,0:10:18.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.73,0:10:27.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,學長！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.27,0:10:34.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,學長...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.55,0:10:39.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.90,0:10:54.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,兩三天前 她就每夜到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.84,0:10:57.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是HIKARI的作法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.18,0:11:01.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,HIKARI 會嗅出人類不滿足的慾望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.25,0:11:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,利用那個做能源來活著
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.38,0:11:05.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不趕快把HIKARI除去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.92,0:11:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她將永遠做夢下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.12,0:11:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一直衰弱 知道死為止
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.86,0:11:17.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜託 與我們一起戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:19.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.94,0:11:24.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是怎樣做才能對抗那怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.21,0:11:27.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想使用“力量”是需要修行的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.55,0:11:29.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天就一起試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.55,0:11:30.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.63,0:11:37.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,遠古時代的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.69,0:11:38.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,將無垢之血化為風
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.03,0:11:40.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,賜你的力量給我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.51,0:11:45.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,後藤！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.24,0:11:47.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,涼 這邊追
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.25,0:11:55.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,破邪之刀...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.01,0:12:13.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小倉泉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.49,0:12:27.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,涼 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.63,0:12:29.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小倉泉 小倉泉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.37,0:12:32.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小倉泉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.06,0:12:46.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,幸好趕上了 次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.26,0:12:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,涼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.59,0:12:50.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好像沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.60,0:12:52.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝你 京華
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.60,0:12:53.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.60,0:12:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我看 這附近忽然傳出不好的氣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.07,0:12:59.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以就趕來看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.94,0:13:03.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎樣 這樣你相信我們的話了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.68,0:13:06.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜託 與我們一起戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.02,0:13:09.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,知道了 我試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.03,0:13:16.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,古時的火焰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.77,0:13:19.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,給這個人治癒的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.44,0:13:24.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣... 她的痛苦的記憶就會消失嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.04,0:13:28.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不知道 但我們也只能這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.80,0:13:40.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以現在本地發生的 連續縱火事件
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.93,0:13:43.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,完全找不出動機呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.40,0:13:46.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原因不明的可疑失火
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.67,0:13:48.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,遊戲中心失火
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.27,0:13:50.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,百貨公司失火
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.81,0:13:52.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,精品店完全燒燬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.94,0:13:54.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你想想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.41,0:13:57.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算這些事件是HIKARI乾的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.22,0:14:01.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他們也不過是附著在 人類的慾望上來行動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.36,0:14:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以縱火的地點與物件
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.23,0:14:05.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都應該有某種共通點的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.63,0:14:11.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,警方發佈的訊息說 是人群多的繁華街道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.51,0:14:14.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,祇有這條訊息是 無法鎖定下次的縱火地點的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.31,0:14:16.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家都加強提防縱火了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.85,0:14:20.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,矢事規模還逐漸增大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.32,0:14:21.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,從這特徵來看...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.65,0:14:24.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我認為一定與HIKARI有關
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.39,0:14:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是不知道 被HIKARI附身的人的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.40,0:14:32.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,目前被認為 最可能矢事的是精品店
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.74,0:14:34.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那些都是表面而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.01,0:14:38.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,動機依然會 被認為是每家店的背後恩怨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.94,0:14:42.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以很難追查了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.15,0:14:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.35,0:14:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我認為被HIKARI附身者 縱火必然有其理由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.76,0:14:53.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在我們只能多蒐集情報了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:56.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對了 京華與涼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.44,0:15:03.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,電影真精彩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.31,0:15:06.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,男主角遇到 啞巴女主角那段真好看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.18,0:15:09.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這哪裡是蒐集資料了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.52,0:15:13.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對 蒐集資料的行動 現在才開始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.26,0:15:18.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我說過 我是開悟的能力者了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.33,0:15:21.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,開悟後可以讀取人心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.47,0:15:23.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使是在人群中也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.63,0:15:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.69,0:15:45.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的力量好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.36,0:15:46.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,光是用心的波動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.70,0:15:49.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就能讓熱戀中的情侶吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.31,0:15:56.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,岩阪真奈美 請加入我們好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.92,0:16:02.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們現在追蹤 街上發生的連續縱火犯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.46,0:16:04.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個事件 不是普通的縱火事件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.13,0:16:06.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這點你也曉得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.53,0:16:09.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果你肯助我們一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.20,0:16:12.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想一定可以抓到縱火犯的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.40,0:16:14.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.75,0:16:17.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,“力量”也可以做那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.48,0:16:20.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對了 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.89,0:16:24.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,昨夜經過前面的精品店時...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.16,0:16:28.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好漂亮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.03,0:16:36.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,紅衣服的女人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.37,0:16:41.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,集合時間到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.25,0:16:43.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起 真奈美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.99,0:16:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們事先有約會了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.92,0:16:49.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,剛才的事 下次再詳細說好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.99,0:16:50.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,京華 關于紅衣服的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.93,0:16:59.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,進入被縱火的精品店的 紅衣女人都像魔女一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.87,0:17:01.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,下一個可能目的...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:05.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,應該事那紅衣女人 進入的六樓的那家店
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.43,0:17:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是嗎 如果HIKARI是女人 常去精品店就很自然了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.57,0:17:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.90,0:17:22.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.57,0:17:26.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你沒有事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.24,0:17:28.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.57,0:17:29.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真奈美 為什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.64,0:17:34.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,京華
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:38.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也想查出縱火犯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.07,0:17:47.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.27,0:17:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要我找上被HIKARI附身的女人 去說服她》
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.20,0:17:55.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,以前我只把自己的“力量” 用在沒意義的事上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.81,0:17:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想到我的力量可以輔助說明人...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.28,0:18:03.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,知道了 我們一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.96,0:18:06.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,涼 你負責保護她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.10,0:18:11.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.27,0:18:38.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,涼 你先去六樓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.27,0:18:38.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.74,0:18:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你沒有問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.74,0:18:44.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我沒有問題 問題事那個使用“言靈”的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.95,0:18:46.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還有涼...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.11,0:19:04.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等一下 前輩 讓我去說服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.71,0:19:05.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.78,0:19:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.11,0:19:08.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是 前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.85,0:19:13.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,被HIKARI附身的人 本來也是普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.65,0:19:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你會使用“言靈”
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.52,0:19:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也許能用你的力量 消除她的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.92,0:19:21.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其它人包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.36,0:19:51.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還是不行 我辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.91,0:19:58.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.19,0:20:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣沒完沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.86,0:20:08.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.06,0:20:10.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你太寂寞了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.66,0:20:12.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,被重要的人背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.66,0:20:15.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你把自己拋棄到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.73,0:20:18.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是逃避一切 獨自一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.48,0:20:20.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一個人活下來的...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.82,0:20:26.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好冷哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.95,0:20:28.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好冷啊 好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.23,0:20:32.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起 我沒注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.45,0:20:49.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.32,0:20:52.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在燃燒 多漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.60,0:21:05.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,燃燒過去能夠滿足你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.07,0:21:07.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣你就滿足了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.14,0:21:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,過去不管再怎樣燃燒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.14,0:21:13.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,回憶都不會消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.69,0:21:14.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不是假人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.89,0:21:16.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是沒靈魂的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.22,0:21:19.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你自己不去改變的話 永遠都改變不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.29,0:21:21.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為世上不全是好人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.83,0:21:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但也不能因此自暴自棄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.50,0:21:26.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你要堅強的活下去呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.63,0:21:28.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不堅強一點的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.97,0:21:32.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只會重覆往事 改變不了事實的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.80,0:21:48.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,泉 這樣沒完沒了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.48,0:22:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.16,0:22:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真奈美
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.37,0:22:12.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真奈美
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.70,0:22:15.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真奈美
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.77,0:22:20.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真奈美
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.98,0:22:24.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.58,0:22:25.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真奈美
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.92,0:22:30.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.99,0:22:33.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是應該的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.19,0:22:36.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,過去我也做了好多壞事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.00,0:22:39.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,理所當然要受懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.14,0:22:41.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不然對不起大家...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.27,0:22:42.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真奈美
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.95,0:22:50.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真奈美
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.48,0:22:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.08,0:22:55.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.29,0:22:58.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,泉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.22,0:22:59.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,涼 真奈美
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.36,0:23:01.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可惡 沒完沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.96,0:23:04.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣下去我們也完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.64,0:23:06.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,涼 真奈美
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.71,0:23:10.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,前輩 剛才謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.18,0:23:13.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你醒了 努力得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.45,0:23:18.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我被HIKARI附身時 我想這一定是天遣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.32,0:23:23.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這跟使用“言靈” 玩弄人心是一樣得
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.12,0:23:25.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我會在這裡死掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.86,0:23:28.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道了 你休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.01,0:23:36.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,開門！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.95,0:23:40.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小倉泉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.49,0:23:43.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看來是趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.03,0:23:51.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.84,0:23:57.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真奈美
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.18,0:23:59.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,涼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.91,0:24:01.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家都沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.92,0:24:02.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.72,0:24:08.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真琴 得救了 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.59,0:24:10.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你又瘦了 喬
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.59,0:24:13.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你最好自己別太自責
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.53,0:24:14.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.60,0:24:16.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是真琴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.73,0:24:18.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我聽小倉泉說了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.33,0:24:20.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然是 如我們想像得厲害術士
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.00,0:24:22.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個人...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.20,0:24:23.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒有得救...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.75,0:24:26.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是我的錯...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.48,0:24:27.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.35,0:24:29.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,最後那瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.55,0:24:31.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她的表情很安詳
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.96,0:24:35.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她一定在那時候 找回自己的心靈了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.49,0:24:40.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比起一直被HIKARI附身 那樣是幸福得多了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.76,0:24:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不這麼認為嗎 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.90,0:24:45.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想應該是的...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.30,0:24:46.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也這麼相信
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.19,0:24:59.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,後會有期 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.93,0:25:05.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喬姐姐 下次再見
